('ed45b72d-61ed-11f1-98fa-60cf847a2597', 'podcast', 'Listen Up!  New Media News on Demand . . .', 'listen-up-new-media-news-on-demand', NULL, '<figure id=\"attachment_1935\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1935\" style=\"width: 500px\" class=\"wp-caption alignleft\"><a href=\"uploads/GMN-7-Hosts-032918.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-1935 size-medium\" src=\"http://www.oldwestburycatalyst.org/wp-content/uploads/GMN-7-Hosts-032918-500x394.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"394\" /></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1935\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Marcy Mendonca and Miguel Castro discussing Net Neutrality on Global Media News.</figcaption></figure>\n<audio class=\"wp-audio-shortcode\" id=\"audio-1932-1\" preload=\"none\" style=\"width: 100%;\" controls=\"controls\"><source type=\"audio/mpeg\" src=\"http://www.oldwestburycatalyst.org/wp-content/uploads/GMN-7-Web-032918.mp3?_=1\" /><a href=\"http://www.oldwestburycatalyst.org/wp-content/uploads/GMN-7-Web-032918.mp3\">http://www.oldwestburycatalyst.org/wp-content/uploads/GMN-7-Web-032918.mp3</a></audio>\n<p><strong>This Week on Global Media News:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Should Twitter Protect the Parkland Teens from Fake Content?</li>\n<li>Newsguard: Brill Start Up Promises to Verify the News.</li>\n<li>The Battle for Net Neutrality: Washington State Takes a Side!</li>\n<li>Will You Pay Youtube for Your Music?</li>\n<li>What Is Tweetdecking? And Why It Will Get You Suspended.</li>\n<li>Insta Adjusts the Feed: What&#8217;s Chronological Got to Do with It?</li>\n<li>Will Reality Truly Be Augmented Marketing?</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Global Media News is a weekly webcast covering new media news from around the world.  GMN is a production of  Media Studies students from the <a href=\"http://www.oldwestbury.edu/\" target=\"_self\">SUNY College @ Old Westbury.</a>   We scour the web for news about new media, journalism and technology.</p>\n<p>Listen to our next podcast streaming live on OWWR: Thursday April 3, 2018 @ 10 am EST.</p>\n<p>Can&#8217;t listen live? Our next podcast  will be posted by 2:00pm, Thursday April 3, 2018.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/GlobalMediaNews\" target=\"_self\">Subscribe Now!</a></p>\n', NULL, 'APPROVED', 'AM327', NULL, '2018-03-29 13:46:29', 0, 'This Week on Global Media News: Should Twitter Protect the Parkland Teens from Fake Content? Newsguard: Brill Start Up Promises to Verify the News. The Battle for Net Neutrality: Washington State Takes a Side! Will You Pay Youtube for Your Music? What Is Tweetdecking? And Why It Will Get You Suspended. Insta Adjusts the Feed:…\n', NULL, NULL, 1),
