('ed46f252-61ed-11f1-98fa-60cf847a2597', 'video', '10 Years of OWTV', '10-years-of-owtv', NULL, '<p>&#8220;&#8230;reporting from OWTV&#8221;. This closing line has been synonymous with aspiring SUNY Old Westbury journalists for the past decade. Come join us in commemorating some of the finest journalists OWTV has had over its ten year run!</p>\n<p><iframe loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/yxZW0VIR8Y8\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Thank you to all the staff, teachers and students who make OWTV a continued success and let&#8217;s hope for another ten years of professional reporting!</p>\n', NULL, 'APPROVED', 'TC527', NULL, '2019-04-08 18:48:48', 0, '“…reporting from OWTV”. This closing line has been synonymous with aspiring SUNY Old Westbury journalists for the past decade. Come join us in commemorating some of the finest journalists OWTV has had over its ten year run! Thank you to all the staff, teachers and students who make OWTV a continued success and let’s hope…\n', NULL, NULL, 15),
('ed473f80-61ed-11f1-98fa-60cf847a2597', 'podcast', 'Podcast: New Media News!', 'podcast-new-media-news', NULL, '<p><a href=\"uploads/GMN-12-square.gif\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-3978\" src=\"uploads/GMN-12-square.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" /></a></p>\n<audio class=\"wp-audio-shortcode\" id=\"audio-3972-1\" preload=\"none\" style=\"width: 100%;\" controls=\"controls\"><source type=\"audio/mpeg\" src=\"http://www.oldwestburycatalyst.org/wp-content/uploads/GMN-12-Web-050919.mp3?_=1\" /><a href=\"http://www.oldwestburycatalyst.org/wp-content/uploads/GMN-12-Web-050919.mp3\">http://www.oldwestburycatalyst.org/wp-content/uploads/GMN-12-Web-050919.mp3</a></audio>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Is Youtube Interactive the Future of Storytelling?</li>\n<li>How to Use  Social to Increase Website Traffic.</li>\n<li>Uber Bot&#8217;s Racist Slur Sparks Outrage.</li>\n<li>Can Live Music Venues Profit from Social Media Engagement?</li>\n<li>Does Game of Thrones Rule Social Media?</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Global Media News is a weekly webcast covering media news from around the world.  GMN is a production of  Media Studies students from the <a href=\"https://www.oldwestbury.edu/\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">SUNY College @ Old Westbury.</a>   We scour the web for news about about the world of media, journalism and technology.</p>\n<p>We will be back in September with another Global Media  News Update!</p>\n<p>Listen to our next  podcast streaming live on <strong><a href=\"http://www.owwr.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">OWWR</a></strong>: Thursday September 5, 2019 @ 10 am EST.</p>\n<p>Can&#8217;t listen live? Our next podcast  will be posted by 3:00pm, September 5, 2019.</p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://feeds.feedburner.com/GlobalMediaNews\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Subscribe Now!</a></strong></p>\n<p>Follow<strong> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/OWWRGMN\" target=\"_blan