('ed481d31-61ed-11f1-98fa-60cf847a2597', 'video', 'Podcasting Media News from Around the World!', '4082', NULL, '<p><a href=\"uploads/GMN-4-GIF.gif\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-4083\" src=\"uploads/GMN-4-GIF.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"360\" height=\"360\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<audio class=\"wp-audio-shortcode\" id=\"audio-4082-1\" preload=\"none\" style=\"width: 100%;\" controls=\"controls\"><source type=\"audio/mpeg\" src=\"http://www.oldwestburycatalyst.org/wp-content/uploads/GMN-4-Web-2019-10-03.mp3?_=1\" /><a href=\"http://www.oldwestburycatalyst.org/wp-content/uploads/GMN-4-Web-2019-10-03.mp3\">http://www.oldwestburycatalyst.org/wp-content/uploads/GMN-4-Web-2019-10-03.mp3</a></audio>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>This week we have media news from France, the U.K., Southeast Asia, Japan and India:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>France: Can the Government Ban Student Smart Devices from School?</li>\n<li>United Kingdom:  The Advertising Standards Authority&#8217;s War on Gender Stereotyping.</li>\n<li>Southeast Asia: Cybersex Trafficking and the Internet.</li>\n<li>Japan:  Will Sega Win Virtual Gold with Olympic Games Tokyo 2020?</li>\n<li>India Shuts Down the Internet and Mobile Phones in Kashmir.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://wcownews.typepad.com/globalmedia/\">Global Media News</a> </strong>is a weekly webcast covering media news from around the world.  GMN is a production of  Media Studies students from the <a href=\"https://www.oldwestbury.edu/\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">SUNY College @ Old Westbury.</a>   We scour the web for news about about the world of media, journalism and technology.</p>\n<p>We will be back next week with another Global Media News Update!</p>\n<p>Listen to our next  podcast streaming live on <strong><a href=\"http://www.owwr.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">OWWR</a></strong>: Thursday October 10, 2019 @ 10 am EST.</p>\n<p>Can&#8217;t listen live? Our next podca