('ed48693c-61ed-11f1-98fa-60cf847a2597', 'podcast', 'Hot Podcast: Global Media News!', 'hot-podcast-global-media-news', NULL, '<p><a href=\"uploads/GMN-6-GIF-Script-Hands-.gif\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-4092\" src=\"uploads/GMN-6-GIF-Script-Hands-.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"320\" height=\"320\" /></a></p>\n<audio class=\"wp-audio-shortcode\" id=\"audio-4090-1\" preload=\"none\" style=\"width: 100%;\" controls=\"controls\"><source type=\"audio/mpeg\" src=\"http://www.oldwestburycatalyst.org/wp-content/uploads/GMN-6-Web-20191017.mp3?_=1\" /><a href=\"http://www.oldwestburycatalyst.org/wp-content/uploads/GMN-6-Web-20191017.mp3\">http://www.oldwestburycatalyst.org/wp-content/uploads/GMN-6-Web-20191017.mp3</a></audio>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Media News from Pakistan, France, Venezuela, Turkey, Japan, and Russia:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Pakistan: Free Media or Censorship?</li>\n<li>France: Will Magelan Rule Podcasting?</li>\n<li>Venezuelan Journalism Under Maduro.</li>\n<li>Turkey: Can Erdoğan Tame the Media?</li>\n<li>Japan: Is Huawei Still a Security Risk?</li>\n<li>Russia: Racial Targeting in the 2016 Election</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"https://wcownews.typepad.com/globalmedia/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Global Media News</a> is a weekly webcast covering media news from around the world.  GMN is a production of  Media Studies students from the <a href=\"https://www.oldwestbury.edu/\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">SUNY College @ Old Westbury.</a>   We scour the web for news about about the world of media, journalism and technology.</p>\n<p>Listen to our next  podcast streaming live on <strong><a href=\"http://www.owwr.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">OWWR</a></strong>: Thursday October 31, 2019 @ 10 am EST.</p>\n<p>Can&#8217;t listen live? Our next podcast  will be posted by 3:00pm, October 31, 2019.</p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://feeds.feedburner.com/GlobalMediaNews\" target=\"