('ed4d8eae-61ed-11f1-98fa-60cf847a2597', 'video', 'Let’s Talk About It-Episode 1', 'lets-talk-about-it-episode-1', NULL, '<p><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Let&#039;s Talk About it - Episode 1\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ZxARLYsmM6Q?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p>In the first episode of Let&#8217;s Talk About It, Nina Crawford talks with Old Westbury students and Media and Journalism Professor Karl Grossman. The Old Westbury community discusses the Gayle King&#8217;s interview about Kobe Bryant and the allegations against him earlier in his career.</p>\n', NULL, 'APPROVED', 'TC527', NULL, '2020-04-17 22:56:16', 0, 'In the first episode of Let’s Talk About It, Nina Crawford talks with Old Westbury students and Media and Journalism Professor Karl Grossman. The Old Westbury community discusses the Gayle King’s interview about Kobe Bryant and the allegations against him earlier in his career.\n', NULL, NULL, 15),
