('ed53f547-61ed-11f1-98fa-60cf847a2597', 'article', 'Calvin O. Butts III Appointed President Emeritus: Recognized for 20 Years of Distingusihed Service', 'calvin-o-butts-iii-appointed-president-emeritus-recognized-for-20-years-of-distingusihed-service', NULL, '<div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div id=\"m_3794523542261156198x_x_x_x_x_x_x_Signature\">\n<div id=\"m_3794523542261156198x_x_x_x_x_x_x_Signature\">\n<div id=\"m_3794523542261156198x_x_x_x_x_x_x_Signature\">\n<div id=\"m_3794523542261156198x_x_x_x_x_x_x_Signature\">\n<div id=\"m_3794523542261156198x_x_x_x_x_x_x_Signature\">\n<div id=\"m_3794523542261156198x_x_x_x_x_x_x_Signature\">\n<div id=\"m_3794523542261156198x_x_x_x_x_x_x_Signature\">\n<div id=\"m_3794523542261156198x_x_x_x_x_x_x_divtagdefaultwrapper\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div id=\"m_3794523542261156198x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_divtagdefaultwrapper\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div id=\"m_3794523542261156198x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_divtagdefaultwrapper\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div id=\"m_3794523542261156198x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_divtagdefaultwrapper\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div id=\"m_3794523542261156198x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_divtagdefaultwrapper\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div id=\"m_3794523542261156198x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_divtagdefaultwrapper\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div id=\"m_3794523542261156198x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_divtagdefaultwrapper\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div id=\"m_3794523542261156198x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_divtagdefaultwrapper\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div id=\"m_3794523542261156198x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_divtagdefaultwrapper\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div id=\"m_3794523542261156198x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_divtagdefaultwrapper\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div id=\"m_3794523542261156198x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_divtagdefaultwrapper\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div id=\"m_3794523542261156198x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_divtagdefaultwrapper\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div id=\"m_3794523542261156198x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_divtagdefaultwrapper\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div id=\"m_3794523542261156198x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_divtagdefaultwrapper\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div id=\"m_3794523542261156198x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_divtagdefaultwrapper\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div id=\"m_3794523542261156198x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_divtagdefaultwrapper\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div id=\"m_3794523542261156198x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_divtagdefaultwrapper\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div id=\"m_3794523542261156198x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_divtagdefaultwrapper\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div id=\"m_3794523542261156198x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_divtagdefaultwrapper\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div id=\"m_3794523542261156198x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_divtagdefaultwrapper\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div id=\"m_3794523542261156198x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_divtagdefaultwrapper\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div id=\"m_3794523542261156198x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_divtagdefaultwrapper\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div id=\"m_3794523542261156198x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_divtagdefaultwrapper\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div id=\"m_3794523542261156198x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_divtagdefaultwrapper\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div id=\"m_3794523542261156198x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_x_divtagdefaultwrapper\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<div>\n<div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_5217\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-5217\" style=\"width: 306px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-5217\" src=\"http://www.oldwestburycatalyst.org/wp-content/uploads/1-332x500.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"306\" height=\"460\" /><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-5217\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Photo Credit: Office of Public Relations and Media</figcaption></figure>\n<p><i>Old Westbury, New York&#8230;September 16, 2020&#8230;  </i>SUNY Chancellor James Malatras and the SUNY Board of Trustees officially appointed Calvin O. Butts, III as President Emeritus of the State University of New York at Old Westbury, in recognition of his 20 years of distinguished service to the college. The appointment was made during the Board&#8217;s September 15, 2020 meeting.</p>\n<div>\n<div>The SUNY resolution appears below:</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<blockquote>\n<div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<